snippet.title: V Rising - Date Reveal Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/games/v-rising/

Enter the world of V Rising on June 11th! Hunt for blood in this dynamic top-down vampire survival action RPG game. Raise a mighty castle that acts as the seat of your power, and remind the world why they should fear the Vampire! Pre-order the Legacy of Castlevania Edition or Complete Edition to get 5 days early access!
